snippet.title: Alan Walker - Faded
snippet.description:
Click below to listen to the first part of my new album, Walkerverse Pt. 1: https://alanwalker.lnk.to/WalkerversePt1

△ Merch @  https://store.alanwalker.no △

Walkers! Thanks for listening. If you want to hear my newest single and the last video in the World of Walker trilogy, "Heading Home," check out the official music video here: https://youtu.be/mfSU_XwEnZA & the LIVE performance here: https://youtu.be/cYxAr_NZF9E

#Faded #AlanWalker #EDM #House #YouAreNotAlone
